Berikut tata cara lengkap Modul B – CI/CD Pipeline ECS Fargate + ECR + CodeBuild + CodeDeploy + CodePipeline (Blue/Green Deployment) sampai berhasil deploy otomatis.

1. Pastikan Infrastruktur Dasar Sudah Ada

Sebelum membuat CI/CD, harus sudah ada:

✅ VPC

✅ Public Subnet 2 AZ

✅ Private Subnet 2 AZ

✅ Internet Gateway

✅ NAT Gateway

✅ ECS Cluster

✅ ECS Service (Fargate)

✅ Application Load Balancer (ALB)

✅ Target Group Blue

✅ Target Group Green

✅ ECR Repository

Jika belum ada, buat dulu.

