19. Uji Blue/Green

Ubah halaman:

res.send("Version 2");

Commit:

git add .
git commit -m "v2"
git push

Lihat:

CodeDeploy

akan muncul:

Blue Environment
↓
Green Environment Created
↓
Health Check Passed
↓
Traffic Shift
↓
Old Environment Terminated
20. Simulasi Rollback

Buat aplikasi error:

throw new Error("Failed");

Push lagi.

CodeDeploy akan:

Deploy Failed
Rollback Started
Traffic Returned to Blue

Ini membuktikan Zero Downtime Deployment berhasil, karena user tetap mengakses versi lama saat versi baru gagal.

